sible to join in the food frenzy! Scalable UI, dyslexia friendly text and colour blindness options are all available.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243830/extras/a88684734d30278b3153fe7915d35551.poster.avif?t=1763038379\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243830/extras/a88684734d30278b3153fe7915d35551.webm?t=1763038379\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1243830/extras/a88684734d30278b3153fe7915d35551.mp4?t=1763038379\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
